<HTML><TITLE>Policy Review Contents, May-June 96 -- Heritage</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" BACKGROUND="/heritage/paperh.jpg">


<IMG SRC="/heritage/revpo.gif" width=169 height=79 ALT=POLICY REVIEW" BORDER=0>
<br>
<img src="pr77.gif" width=200 height=267 align=right>
&#160; &#160;<b>May-June 1996</b><br>
&#160; &#160;Number 77<br>
&#160; &#160;Published by<br>
