<H1>Thomas G. West</H1>
</CENTER>

<p>
Thomas G. West is Professor of Politics at the University of Dallas, Irving, Texas.  He is the 
editor of <i>Algernon Sidney's Discourses Concerning Government</i> (Liberty Press, 1993), and 
author of <i>Plato's Apology of Socrates</i> (Cornell University Press, 1979), and numerous articles on 
political theory and the American Founding.  


