   <H1>Patrick J. Garrity</H1>

</CENTER>

Patrick J. Garrity has recently returned to the Los Alamos Scientific Laboratories in Los Alamos, New Mexico, where he has been a senior policy analyst since 1985. Dr. Garrity was a fellow at the Johns Hopkins University Foreign Policy Institute in 
Washington, D.C. from 1994 until early 1996. He has published widely on 
international affairs and American foreign policy.

<p>
Dr. Garrity holds the M.A. and Ph.D. in Government from the Claremont Graduate School. 


