<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/townhall/FRC/whois/donodoc.html 204.71.237.92 19970115112128 text/html 31281
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 15-Jan-97 11:21:42 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 24-Apr-96 15:22:41 GMT
Content-length: 31091
