<HTML>
<TITLE>Featured Speeches</TITLE>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">
<TITLE>Featured Speeches of Ronald Reagan</TITLE>

<H2> <CENTER><I>Featured Speeches of Ronald Reagan</I> </CENTER> </H2>
<CENTER><HR SIZE=3 WIDTH=50%></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/hall_of_fame/reagan/speech/challeng.htm">In Response
to the Challenger Disaster</A>
