<HEAD>

<TITLE>EDO Combat Systems Home Page</TITLE>

<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Kehoe, White, Savage & Company, Inc.">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../gif/combat.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> </CENTER>
<H2><CENTER>Welcome to the<BR>EDO Combat Systems Home Page</CENTER>
</H2>

<P>
<CENTER>[ <A href="products/products.html">Products and Services</A>
| <A href="team.html">Our Team</A> | <A href="contact.html">Contact Us</A>
| <A HREF="../../invest/prlsmenu.html">EDO News</A> ] </CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>[ <A HREF="../defehome.html">EDO Defense and Space Systems Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="../../index.html">EDO Corporation Home Page</A> ] </CENTER>
<P><HR>

<P>
EDO Combat Systems designs, develops and produces ASW sonar, digital
data link, and command and control systems for both domestic and
international customers. EDO has been a supplier of ASW sonar
systems for more than 40 years. It is emerging today as a supplier of low-cost, robust tactical data link systems for use
in shipboard, aircraft, mobile shore-based, and command center
environments.
<P>
EDO Combat Systems provides complete logistics support for its
products, including installation and training, documentation,
spare and repair parts, and field service throughout the world.
<P><HR>

<P>
<CENTER>[ <A HREF="../defehome.html">EDO Defense and Space Systems Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="../../index.html">EDO Corporation Home Page</A> ] </CENTER>
