<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../gif/acoustic.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> </CENTER>
<H2><CENTER>Welcome to the<BR>EDO Acoustic Products Home Page</CENTER>
</H2>

<P>
<CENTER>[ <A HREF="products/acouprod.html">Products and Services</A>
| <A HREF="team.html">Our Team</A> | <A HREF="contact.html">Contact Us</A>
| <A HREF="../../invest/prlsmenu.html">EDO News</A> ] </CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>[ <A HREF="../induhome.html">EDO Industrial Products Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="../../index.html">EDO Corporation Home Page</A> ] </CENTER>
<P><HR>

<P>
For more than 30 years EDO Acoustic Products has provided high
quality underwater acoustic transducers, navigation and communication
products to the world's modern naval warships and commercial concerns.
Our products include:
<UL>
<LI>Velocity Measurement Systems
<LI>Acoustic Transducers, Underwater Navigation and Communications
Systems
<LI>Active Force Control SubSystems for Precision Machining<BR>

</UL>

<P>
EDO is committed to preserving and expanding this legacy of successful
programs, cost effective products and satisfied customers through:
<UL>
<LI><B>Experienced Personnel:</B> We have assembled an exceptional team of experienced managers, dedicated engineers and MIL qualified
production leaders to ensure that only the highest quality, cost
effective products are designed, manufactured, and delivered to
our customers.</UL>
<P><UL>

<LI><B>World Class Facilities:</B> Full production facilities
including computer aided design, manufacturing, and complete acoustic
and electronic testing facilities, allow rapid prototyping of developmental
systems.</UL>
<P><UL>

<LI><B>Vertical Integration Capabilities:</B> EDO's complete in-house
capability allows us to produce all components necessary for the
many stages of manufacturing, from production of piezoelectric
ceramics used in the transducers, to the complete integrated electronics system
ready for installation. We are able to maintain greater control
over schedule and cost through vertical integration of the entire
manufacturing process.</UL>
<P><UL>

<LI><B>Commitment:</B> A total commitment to the needs of our
customers drives EDO Acoustics Division to meet the most demanding
requirements. A unique experience base and the highest standards of engineering
excellence enables us to consistently deliver superior products.
</UL>
<P>EDO Acoustic Products and EDO Ceramics constitute EDO Western Corporation, a wholly-owned subsidiary of EDO Corporation.
