<TITLE>EDO ANGI Home Page</TITLE>
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Kehoe, White, Savage & Company, Inc.">

</HEAD>

<BODY>


<CENTER><IMG SRC="../../gif/angi.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> </CENTER>
<P><H2><CENTER>Welcome to the<BR>EDO ANGI Home Page</CENTER></H2>

<HR><P><Center><H3><I><B>NEWS FLASH: EDO Corporation has announced the decision to discontinue its participation in the alternative energy business.  Therefore, it is seeking interested investors for its energy-related businesses.  Anyone interested in acquiring EDO's interest in either or both of these businesses should contact <A HREF="mailto:investor.relations@edocorp.com ">Mr. William J. Frost at EDO Corporation, (718) 321-4000</A>.</B></I></H3></CENTER><HR>


<CENTER> [ <A HREF="products/angiprod.html">Products and Services</A>
| <A HREF="team.html">Our Team</A> | <A HREF="contact.html">Contact Us</A>
| <A HREF="../../invest/prlsmenu.html">EDO News</A> ] </CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER>[ <A HREF="../discont.html">Discontinued Operations Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="../../index.html">EDO Corporation Home Page</A> ] </CENTER>
<P><HR>

<P>
EDO ANGI is a full service packager and manufacturer of compressed
natural gas refueling stations and vehicle conversion equipment.
Established in 1983 as Automotive Natural Gas Inc. the company
is a true pioneer in the alternative fuels industry and has installed equipment at
more than 250 CNG refueling stations across the country, and distributed
approximately 14,000 conversion kits to a broad spectrum of vehicle
markets including passenger cars, trucks, school buses, forklifts,
and marine vessels.
<P>
In addition to using the finest componentry available to construct
stations that range in capacity from 10 to 2000 scfm, EDO ANGI
has developed its own superior line of time and fast fill dispensing
systems and fuel management systems for accurate records of usage.
As part of the EDO Corporation team, EDO ANGI also has access
to the complete inventory of LiteRider&#174; NGV cylinders, the
lightest, and highest volume cylinder on the world market
<P>
To support EDO ANGI products in the field, the company has established
one of the most respected customer service programs in the industry.
Service contracts are offered as an option to each sale and include
a four hour response time from field service engineers trained
by EDO ANGI and equipped with EDO parts. A 24-hour, toll-free
hotline is also serviced by trained technicians, qualified to
respond to a full range of inquiries on vehicle systems and refueling
stations.
<P>
<A HREF="p-plant.html"><B>Click Here</B></A> to see a photograph of the
EDO ANGI Manufacturing Plant
<P>
<A HREF="p-maps.html"><B>Click Here</B></A> to see the locations of 250
ANGI Supplied Stations Sites Across the U.S.
<P>
<A HREF="custlist.html">EDO ANGI Customer List</A> 
<P>
<A HREF="../canada/canahome.html">EDO (Canada) Ltd. Home Page - LiteRider&#174; Cylinders</A>
<P>EDO Automotive Natural Gas, Inc. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of EDO Energy, Inc. which, in turn, is a wholly-owned subsidiary of EDO Corporation.
