<H2>
  <CENTER>
    Welcome to the<BR>
    EDO Corporation Home Page
  </CENTER>
</H2>
<CENTER>
<H3><A HREF="http://quote.yahoo.com/quotes?SYMBOLS=edo&detailed=t"><B><I>Current EDO Stock Quote (NYSE:EDO)</I></B></A></H3></center>
<center> <H3>
<A HREF="invest/releases/hotnews1.html"><B><I>NEWS FLASH:</I></B> EDO Corporation Awarded Contract For GPS Satellite Earth Sensor; Total Contract With Options Valued at $28 Million </A>
  </b></H3>
</H2>

<hr>
<P ALIGN=Center>
[ <A HREF="defense/defehome.html">EDO Defense and Space Systems Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="indust/induhome.html">EDO Industrial Products Home Page</A> ]
<P ALIGN=Center>
[ <A HREF="invest/irmenu.html">Investor &amp; Financial Information</A> |
<A HREF="invest/prlsmenu.html">EDO Press Releases</A> ]
<P ALIGN=Center>
[ <A HREF="root/offices.html">Corporate Directory</A> |
<A HREF="root/talk2edo.html">Talk to EDO</A> ]
</Center>
  <HR>
<P>
EDO is principally a supplier of proprietary advanced electro-optical,
electronic, mechanical, acoustic and composite products to major prime defense
contractors and commercial original equipment manufacturers. EDO also serves
the domestic and international defense markets as a prime contractor for
military systems.
<P>
Our Web pages provide information about the corporation, its divisions, and
the advanced capabilities of the people who operate our business units.
<P>
<CENTER>
  <STRONG>Please click below for more information.</STRONG>
</CENTER>
<P>
<A HREF="defense/defehome.html">EDO Defense and Space Systems Division</A>
<UL>
  <P>
  <LI>
    <A HREF="defense/combat/combhome.html">EDO Combat Systems</A> -- Designer
    and builder of special platform equipment and open data processing systems
    to support the modern war fighter.
  <LI>
    <A HREF="defense/optics/optihome.html">EDO Electro-Optics Systems (Barnes
    Engineering)</A> -- A producer of infrared earth horizon sensors for the
    satellite industry.
  <LI>
    <A HREF="defense/marine/marihome.html">EDO Marine and Aircraft Systems</A>
    -- EDO Marine and Aircraft Systems is focused on defense products and
    technologies for the U. S. and foreign nations with an emphasis on Mine
    Countermeasures and Suspension and Release Equipment for military aircraft.
</UL>
<P>
<A HREF="indust/induhome.html">EDO Industrial Products Division</A>
<UL>
  <P>
  <LI>
    <A HREF="indust/acoustic/acouhome.html">EDO Acoustic Products</A> -- Designer
    and manufacturer of acoustic navigation and communications products including
    velocity measurement products, acoustic and underwater navigation and
    communications systems.
<LI>
    <A HREF="indust/ceramics/cerahome.html">EDO Ceramics</A> -- Developer and
    manufacturer of specialized active piezoelectric ceramic components and devices.
  <LI>
    <A HREF="indust/fiber/fibehome.html">EDO Fiber Science</A> -- Developer and
    manufacturer of high strength, light weight, filament wound pressure tanks
    for gas and liquid containment and large fiber reinforced wind turbine blades
    and stator cores for electrical power generation systems.
</UL>
<hr>
<P>
<I><A HREF="indust/discont.html">Discontinued Operations:  Alternative Energy Businesses</A></I>
<P>EDO Corporation has announced the decision to discontinue its participation in the alternative energy business.  Therefore, it is seeking interested investors for its energy-related businesses.  Anyone interested in acquiring EDO's interest in either or both of these businesses should contact <A HREF="mailto:investor.relations@edocorp.com ">Mr. William J. Frost at EDO Corporation, (718) 321-4000</A>.
<UL>
  <P>
<LI>
    <A HREF="indust/angi/angihome.html">EDO ANGI</A> -- A full service packager
    and manufacturer of compressed natural gas refueling stations and vehicle
    conversion equipment.
  <LI>
    <A HREF="indust/canada/canahome.html">EDO (Canada) Ltd.</A> -- Developer
    and manufacturer of the all composite, light weight and high volume EDO
    LiteRider&reg; compressed natural gas cylinder for use on board vehicles
    powered by natural gas.
</UL>
