<H2><CENTER>Investor Information and SEC Documents</CENTER></H2>

<P>
<CENTER>[ <A HREF="../index.html">EDO Corporation Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="irmenu.html">Investor Relations Home Page</A> ]</CENTER>
<P><HR>

<H3>Investor Information</H3>

<P>
<A HREF="docs/953qsrpt.html">Report to Shareholders for the Third Quarter Ended September 30, 1995</A>

<H3>SEC Documents in EDGAR Format</H3>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="secdocs/fy96-q1.txt">FY 96 First Quarter Report on Form 10-Q</A>
<I>(22068 Bytes</I>)
<LI><A HREF="secdocs/fy95-10k.txt">FY 95 Annual Report on Form 10-K </A>
<I>(144517 Bytes</I>)
<LI><A HREF="secdocs/fy95-q3.txt">FY 95 Third Quarter Report on Form 10-Q</A>
<I>(29370 Bytes</I>)
<LI><A HREF="secdocs/fy95-q2.txt">FY 95 Second Quarter Report on Form 10-Q</A>
<I>(33803 Bytes</I>)
<LI><A HREF="secdocs/fy95-q1.txt">FY 95 First Quarter Report on Form 10-Q</A>
