<TITLE>Press Release: Ira Kaplan Appointed Executive Vice President and Chief Operating
 Officer of EDO Corporation </TITLE>
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Kehoe, White, Savage &amp; Company, Inc."></HEAD>

<!-- $MVD$:COLOR("2","0","Black") -->
