   <title>Press Release: EDO Corporation Awarded $2 million Follow-On Contract by Sparton Corporation; EDO to Produce Ceramic Components used in U. S. Navy SSQ 62C Sonobuoy Program </title>
   <meta name="AUTHOR" content="Kehoe, White, Savage & Company, Inc.">
   <meta name="GENERATOR" content="Mozilla/2.01Gold (Win32)">
